#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_books/chiseled_bookshelf.lua:253
msgid "Chiseled Bookshelf"
msgstr "雕纹书架"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_books/chiseled_bookshelf.lua:254
msgid "Chiseled bookshelf holds up to six books."
msgstr "雕纹书架最多可放置六本书。"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_books/init.lua:15
msgid "Book"
msgstr "书籍"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_books/init.lua:16
msgid "Books are used to make bookshelves and book and quills."
msgstr "书可用于制作书架以及书与羽毛笔。"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_books/init.lua:39
msgid "“@1”"
msgstr "“@1”"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_books/init.lua:41
msgid "Copy of “@1”"
msgstr "“@1”的抄本"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_books/init.lua:43
msgid "Copy of Copy of “@1”"
msgstr "“@1”的再抄本"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_books/init.lua:45
msgid "Tattered Book"
msgstr "残书"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_books/init.lua:47 mods/ITEMS/mcl_books/init.lua:123
msgid "by @1"
msgstr "由@1撰写"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_books/init.lua:64
msgid "Sign"
msgstr "告示牌"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_books/init.lua:65 mods/ITEMS/mcl_books/init.lua:78
msgid "Done"
msgstr "完成"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_books/init.lua:84
msgid "Book and Quill"
msgstr "书与羽毛笔"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_books/init.lua:85
msgid "Write down some notes"
msgstr "写下一些笔记"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_books/init.lua:86
msgid "This item can be used to write down some notes."
msgstr "这件物品可用来写下一些笔记。"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_books/init.lua:88
msgid ""
"Hold it in the hand, then rightclick to read the current notes and edit "
"then. You can edit the text as often as you like. You can also sign the book "
"which turns it into a written book which you can stack, but it can't be "
"edited anymore."
msgstr ""
"将它拿在手中，然后右键点击可阅读当前笔记并进行编辑。你可以随意多次编辑文本。"
"你也可以在书上签名，这样它就变成了一本已写好的书，能进行堆叠，但不能再被编辑"
"了。"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_books/init.lua:90
msgid ""
"A book can hold up to @1 characters. The title length is limited to @2 "
"characters."
msgstr "一本书最多可容纳 @1个字母。标题长度限制为 @2个字母。"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_books/init.lua:111
msgid ""
"Text is @1 characters too long for one book.\n"
"It will be capped at @2 characters."
msgstr ""
"对于一本书来说，@1 个字母太长。\n"
"上限为 @2个字母。"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_books/init.lua:121
msgid "Enter book title:"
msgstr "输入书名："

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_books/init.lua:125
msgid "Sign and Close"
msgstr "签名并关闭"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_books/init.lua:127
msgid "Note: The book will no longer be editable after signing"
msgstr "注意：签名后，该书将无法再被编辑"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_books/init.lua:128
msgid "Cancel"
msgstr "取消"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_books/init.lua:139
msgid "Nameless Book"
msgstr "佚书"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_books/init.lua:173
msgid "Written Book"
msgstr "成书"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_books/init.lua:175
msgid ""
"Written books contain some text written by someone. They can be read and "
"copied, but not edited."
msgstr ""
"已写好的书包含一些由某人写下的文字。它们可以被阅读和复制，但不能被编辑。"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_books/init.lua:177
msgid "Hold it in your hand, then rightclick to read the book."
msgstr "把书拿在手中，然后右键点击阅读该书。"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_books/init.lua:180
msgid ""
"To copy the text of the written book, place it into the crafting grid "
"together with a book and quill (or multiple of those) and craft. The written "
"book will not be consumed. Copies of copies can not be copied."
msgstr ""
"要复制已写好的书的文本，将其与书和羽毛笔（或多个）一起放入制作网格中然后进行"
"合成操作。已写好的书不会被消耗掉。副本的副本不能被复制。"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_books/init.lua:282 mods/ITEMS/mcl_books/init.lua:318
msgid "Bookshelf"
msgstr "书架"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_books/init.lua:297
msgid "Inventory"
msgstr "库存"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_books/init.lua:319
msgid "Bookshelves are used for decoration."
msgstr "书架用于装饰。"
